Magic v2 spells (for World Book)

Notebooks (.ipynb version)
===========================

Some cells have spells.

Some cells check the difficulty.

Some cells check the RST representation.

Spell Module (.py version)
==========================

Each spell book is a definition of spells and a main program.

Produces details of the spell to help debug the difficulty budget.

::

    % python spells/some_book.py debug "spell name"


Spell Document (.txt version)
=============================

Produces RST-formatted documents for inclusion in a rule book

::

    % python spells/some_book.py display

Maps and drawings.

